  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "Credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump. Thirteen ASME V&V 40 credibility factors evaluated at Model Risk Level 5. Package conforms to Minimal profile; intended-use scope is not declared.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5-req",
